name: Amazing Princess Gymnastics Switch
description:
Tap to help the gymnastics princess flip cross through the right color pattern from multi-colored spinning rings and obstacles! If you hit or pass the wrong color , the challenge fails and need to restart the game again .

Heaps of color challenging levels with hundreds of different colorful patterns of obstacles are waiting for you to cross through!

Amazing Gymnastics Switch game requires fast reaction , how many coloured obstacles and rings can you go cross? Accept the challenge today!
